name: World History Collection (EBSCO)
description: World History Collection offers a global look at history with content from Africa, Asia, North and South America, Europe and the Middle East. Full text dates as far back as 1964. The information sources cover a wide range of historical topics including anthropology, art, culture, economics, government, heritage, military, politics, regional issues, and more. In addition to the full text, indexing and abstracts are provided for all journals in the collection.
